  "title": "[사당동이수한방다이어트한의원]복부다이어트/뱃살다이어트",
  "addDate": "2013. 3. 12.",
  "categoryNo": "11",
  "parentCategoryNo": "11",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110162646546",
  "html_size": 192651,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110162646546\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110162646546\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<DIV class=view style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&#65279;</SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;[복부 다이어트/뱃살다이어트/한방다이어트]</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">한해가 시작되면 계획을 세우게 됩니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">여성분들은 다이어트가 첫번째로 계획을 세우게 되지만 </SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">몇일 하다가 말게 되는게 다이어트 입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">뱃살은 건강에 나쁜영향을 미치기 때문에 반드시 해결해야 할 것입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b97355d4e93738ed.png\" width=\"404\" height=\"302\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 404px; rheight: 302px\" id=\"20130312_297/isuhani_1363062299963PbMwq_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%CE%BA%F1%B8%B81.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b97355d4e93738ed.png\"></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">복부비만이란, 체지방이 복부에 집중적으로 쌓인 것으로 한국인의 허리둘레 기준으로 남자는 35.4인치 이상,</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">여자는 33.5인치 이상인경우 복부비만 이라합니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">복부비만에는 두가지로 나눠지는데 내장형 복부비만과 피하형 복부비만 입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">내장형 복부비만은 체강 내 지방 축적이 심한경우로 음주, 야식, 운동부족이 원인이 되어 발생하는 경우가 많고</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">피하형 복부비만은 여성형 복부비만으로 복벽에 피하지방이 과하게 축적되어 있는 상태로 출산이나 변비</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">잦은 다이어트 실패, 자궁허냉, 폭식, 호르몬의 변화로 인해 발생 하게 됩니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84ba26442925e20a.png\" width=\"476\" height=\"327\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 476px; rheight: 327px\" id=\"20130312_92/isuhani_1363062395201zuWdw_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%CE%BA%F1%B8%B8%C3%BC%C1%DF%B0%E83.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84ba26442925e20a.png\"></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">뱃살은 내장지방이 많으면 지방간, 대장암, 유방암&nbsp; 성인병 위험이 증가 하므로 복부비만은 반드시 </SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">치료해야 할 문제 입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #009e25; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">이수한의원에서</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #009e25; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\"> </SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #009e25; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">뱃살, 복부비만&nbsp; 빼는 방법</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/74f8b70cd490c3fd.jpg\" width=\"265\" height=\"217\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 265px; rheight: 217px\" id=\"20130312_277/isuhani_1363062451180RxUK0_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BA%CE%C7%D720130214_151615.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/74f8b70cd490c3fd.jpg\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ee775ce0b80ad92.jpg\" width=\"265\" height=\"217\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 265px; rheight: 217px\" id=\"20130312_153/isuhani_13630624845509Ox2R_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BA%C0%C4%A720130128_101412.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ee775ce0b80ad92.jpg\"></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f98db258d3085d50.jpg\" width=\"265\" height=\"217\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 265px; rheight: 217px\" id=\"20130312_90/isuhani_1363062522443owfji_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%BA%B9%BA%CE%BE%C6%C0%CC%BD%C3%C6%BC20130214_152303.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f98db258d3085d50.jpg\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ad9df48f9c5dd432.jpg\" width=\"265\" height=\"217\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 265px; rheight: 217px\" id=\"20130312_234/isuhani_1363062555372TpGdy_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C0%E7%C0%FC%C4%A720130214_152530.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ad9df48f9c5dd432.jpg\"></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp; - </SPAN><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">다이어트 한약</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;이수한의원에 복부다이어트 한약은 체지방이 과잉축적 된것을 분해 시켜줍니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 또한 어혈이나 체내 독소 배출을 도와주고 식욕을 억제하며, 기초대사량을 높임으로 뱃살&nbsp;빼는 데 효과가 좋습니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - </SPAN><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">지방 분해 약침</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 이수한의원의 지방 분해 약침은 뱃살에 주입함으로써 체지방을 분해하고 </SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 셀룰라이트를 제거 할수 있도록 도와주는 방법입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - </SPAN><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">지방 분해 전기침</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 이수한의원의 지방 분해 전기침은 체지방이 축적된 뱃살에&nbsp; 비만침을 놓고</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 미세한 전류를 통과시켜 지방층을 자극을 합니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - </SPAN><STRONG><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">부항 요법</SPAN></STRONG></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 이수한의원의 부항 요법은 혈액순환/기혈순환을 원활하게 하는데 필요한 방법이고</SPAN></P>\r\n<P><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 어혈과 같은 독소와 노폐물을 체외로 배출시켜 내장지방 분해를 할 수 있도록 도와 줍니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130311_188/isuhani_1363007351895Aw3Mk_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%CE%BA%F1%B8%B85.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"302\" height=\"305\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 302px; rheight: 305px\" id=\"20130311_188/isuhani_1363007351895Aw3Mk_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%CE%BA%F1%B8%B85.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6349612')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130311_188/isuhani_1363007351895Aw3Mk_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%CE%BA%F1%B8%B85.PNG?type=w3\"></P>\r\n<P>&nbsp; </P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">복부 다이어트에서 중요한 식이요법과 운동요법은 필수입니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">굶는 다이어트는 요요현상이 나타 나므로 주의 하셔야합니다</SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center><pzp-pc-layout class=\"_naverVideo _vnl\" vid=\"8EDC603B29B37B7AB0398A8349F8D335AF36\" key=\"V12150ff8cd207c9a54886adfd10800810e81b3ca0f152bf85636e315ef8fe88f8e056adfd10800810e81\" outKeyMode=\"false\" hasLink=\"true\" logNo=\"110162646546\" domain-or-blogId=\"isuhani\" style=\"width:512px; height:321px;\">\n  <pzp-pc-header class=\"pzp-pc__header\">\n    <pzp-pc-content-info class=\"pzp-pc__content-info\">\n      <pzp-pc-content-title></pzp-pc-content-title>\n      <pzp-pc-play-count></pzp-pc-play-count>\n    </pzp-pc-content-info>\n    <pzp-pc-toolbar class=\"pzp-pc__toolbar\">\n        <pzp-pc-share-button class=\"pzp-pc__share-button\" data-style=\"type_player\" data-player-target-id=\"spi_player_8EDC603B29B37B7AB0398A8349F8D335AF36\"></pzp-pc-share-button>\n    </pzp-pc-toolbar>\n  </pzp-pc-header>\n<span id=\"spi_player_8EDC603B29B37B7AB0398A8349F8D335AF36\" class=\"pzp-pc__social-plugin-container\"></span>\n</pzp-pc-layout>\n \r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=center>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P>\r\n<P>&nbsp;</P></DIV></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
